{"tid":194932,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"四個小生日本玩命，挑戰自由行極限（求指教）","createTime":"2017-04-10T10:11:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T05:01:35.000Z","uid":104167,"like":3,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c74b015b04b0f40fe1bc63a479dfdef4749dc8a9","tid":194932,"uid":104167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:11:37.000Z","msg":"Plan左尼緊八月頭去日本自駕遊，由關西開始玩到東京，最後東京番香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nplan左一開始順住去奈良&gt;大阪&gt;兵庫&gt;京都&gt;福井&gt;岐阜（中途會經名古屋）&gt;愛知&gt;靜岡&gt;群馬&gt;經埼玉&gt;最後東京<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9QiJ532.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9QiJ532.jpg&h=5bb01741&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n簡介一下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地四個都係男仔尼嘅，18－20歲，相約左每一年都會一齊去一次旅行，今年已經係第二次，上年去左泰國，成日都聽到話有人去旅行會嘈交，會破壞感情，但我地四個小生就相反，希望用一年一度嘅旅程去加強大家之間感情嘅連繫。非gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對於日本嘅印象都係頭文字D呀，魚生，動漫呀果D，了解唔多， 亦唔係話對動漫沉迷，但當然都會去行下<br />\n因為唔太了解日本，所以想跪求問下咁多位chings 有冇咩好路數，靚嘅景點，好味嘅野食，好玩嘅地方指教下，等我地唔好係咁中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"616bc6ccb81a3faa925183d065f1a4a4a2e15b1e","tid":194932,"uid":23619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:13:16.000Z","msg":"尼你老母"},{"pid":"15fc2c3e7ddde8b370cfca324826c431e8e15cc1","tid":194932,"uid":104167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:15:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>尼你老母</blockquote><br />\nSor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"583a8502bb2275117f044a6be8b37812d30abc65","tid":194932,"uid":55513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:21:30.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad716c0d1f065e9fde977f912822b7176e3414b3","tid":194932,"uid":48