車，一定唔會夠精神</blockquote><br />\n8日一條友渣車.仲有18－20歲.我當無渣大膽車得兩年牌.極限運動?<br />\n去盡無悔?<br />\n仲要大大聲話自己係伸手黨</blockquote><br />\n呢d咪就係乞衣囉<br />\n<br />\nbtw留名等睇新聞日本有自駕遊人士交通意外冚車剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔好累到當地人呀仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce9829df67b131ef11bac8f20ae45da58b8fa965","tid":194932,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:48:12.000Z","msg":"戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8069e7b54f016e2ff36e6e61b57578fb8d98f801","tid":194932,"uid":10533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:55:07.000Z","msg":"我六月都去日本自駕遊喎<br />\n四國&gt;廣島&gt;京阪神&gt;北陸&gt;東京<br />\n不過我就咩都plan好哂啦 去22日 你去得個8日 玩得到啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要得1個揸車 勸你都係算把啦<br />\n到時上黎打遊記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea5fb958a2266543c627c36797cc154d20ba159","tid":194932,"uid":50980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T00:47:43.000Z","msg":"大家唔好咁衰  俾下鼓勵後生仔   記住買足保險   撞車唔好累街坊  有咩事嗌自己係中國人  小日本彈開"},{"pid":"aca4d919c876cd4d6db9170ed9c781b8429baa28","tid":194932,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T00:50:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家唔好咁衰  俾下鼓勵後生仔   記住買足保險   撞車唔好累街坊  有咩事嗌自己係中國人  小日本彈開</blockquote><br />\n索性插支五星旗係車，打橫行都重得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"226bd2da75bf0cd4eee0a2dbd04e62a648045204","tid":194932,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T01:07:38.000Z","msg":"你地唔係去日本玩，係玩緊揸車個條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c6f4b3e1f00a8869471b32dbb210cb895668ce","tid":194932,"uid":57205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T01:39:59.000Z","msg":"去咁多地方得一個渣車等上新聞"},{"pid":"9c6de63f9a72281074c322e126caef06599768e5","tid":194932,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T01:48:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地唔係去日本玩，係玩緊揸車個條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n換轉我係揸車個個真係喊三聲<br />\n最好就輕輕炒一炒冚車無得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dcabc6b27f1b4dfd6d0a45c45b875dbe49705e6","tid":194932,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T02:07:01.000Z","msg":"去元朗天水圍自駕遊算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4aea993e2fe07508d0842435544fb81b6d94da","tid":194932,"uid":44377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T02:28:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你地唔係去日本玩，係玩緊揸車個條友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n換轉我係揸車個個真係喊三聲<br />\n最好就輕輕炒一炒冚車無得玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係唔知點解可以PLAN到呢個行程<br />\n最初無睇清楚覺得都OK, 但原來得8日, 日日除左揸車之外仲有咩可以&quot;玩&quot;到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n後來見仲話打算係車訓, 我真係唔識講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果真係去左架話, 希望佢地寫返個遊記, 好想睇"},{"pid":"76b83b37ad4b78789c76b2e144b84cf13005bcef","tid":194932,"uid":7291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T02:39:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>首先<br />\n去日本除咗北海道冇咩必要自駕</blockquote><br />\n戇駕 沖繩呢 最北果d都無鐵路到<br />\n<br />\n你話bus tour咁北海道都有"},{"pid":"2fabd30bdd73f841824566d6897cf219a80dc81e","tid":194932,"uid":23416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T02:40:31.000Z","msg":"咁就叫極限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人唔笑狗都吠"},{"pid":"1455f6b68633eee74e8ce22a7d9c83122de7419f","tid":194932,"uid":38173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T02:44:41.000Z","msg":"屌你老母以為咩咁巴閉又玩命又極限<br />\n<br />\n入到黎得啖笑<br />\n<br />\n對你地黎講咁就叫極限, 真係擔心你地將來點面對呢個社會"},{"pid":"41970767d90e7bca603d317007d97523bbe836ed","tid":194932,"uid":1391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T02:48:08.000Z","msg":"8日7夜去咁多地方<br />\n連checkin 既時間都冇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6be5ba02b64a7bd2feed920b3b40b82f39af2d","tid":194932,"uid":93091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T02:58:17.000Z","msg":"咁都叫玩命，試過帶帳篷去四國瞓街四十幾日，徒步行，真係差啲死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 8日一定唔夠玩，就算淨係去啲出名嘢東大寺、名古屋城都只能打卡，唔可以細心睇<br />\n個人認為名古屋無咩睇，除非係古城迷，如果都係可以唔洗去，留返多啲係京都或奈良好過"},{"pid":"6fcd3492a4d12df4d5621181120bddf2820f675c","tid":194932,"uid":49992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T02:59:10.000Z","msg":"咁我去跳skydive 算係咩？"},{"pid":"853296fea74645c8931f1152c3b2ac1288b06fd6","tid":194932,"uid":78533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊忽玩命 share旅行plan?"},{"pid":"8dfefdc2795e47da70d9354feb61c887873b89e7","tid":194932,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:01:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aceb77ddf79a01636b099a332218aef4d2210ad6","tid":194932,"uid":2792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:30:10.000Z","msg":"個簡介勁似5P D MK故"},{"pid":"3868aaa4fe7c4c2deacbc91200802964a21937e4","tid":194932,"uid":11254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:36:44.000Z","msg":"揸車個個就真係玩命喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe5696c013e7b26f6eb5f8721dea066b6412a430","tid":194932,"uid":66075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:39:45.000Z","msg":"玩命?極限?<br />\n我當堂嚇一跳，然後得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76eef463fe888fcd0d15d0361937ebeff207a397","tid":194932,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:49:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>玩命?極限?<br />\n我當堂嚇一跳，然後得啖笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對揸車個個就真係玩命既......."},{"pid":"7968772485187f9a22cd21261344264efc39e53d","tid":194932,"uid":64481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T03:58:43.000Z","msg":"好心認真計劃下先啦屌你老母<br />\n全程得一條友揸<br />\n攰得滯炒車<br />\n唔方唔玩命<br />\n仲要四條友完全唔熟日本<br />\n就學人鳩遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e0db3e28f83cac94d867495a1ac922a0ed09d05","tid":194932,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:19:13.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f078bfac2de13172f8ffed382c4fac788b6830e6","tid":194932,"uid":104763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T04:21:23.000Z","msg":"你負評夠多了 我就此拜別"}]}